      "content": "i know it's not \"the answer\"... everything says it isn't. but it's just so heavy. it's like i'm carrying this massive weight and every day is just more weight being added. i look at the people around me, all these successful researchers, and i just feel like an impostor who ran out of luck. i don't see a version of the future where i actually feel okay again. it just feels like i'm stuck in this endless loop of failing. everything feels so pointless now.",
