      "content": "it's just hard to believe in a \"path forward\" when everything i built is gone. it's like i'm just a hollow shell. even if i tried to start over, the thought of having to fight this hard again, just to potentially fail again... it's exhausting. i just want to find some peace. i want the weight to just stop being so much. i'm just so, so tired of fighting it.",
